  "title": "E-commerce demo: autocomplete=off not set",
  "body": "**Do you want to request a *feature* or report a *bug*?**\r\n\r\nBug.\r\n\r\n**Bug: What is the current behavior?**\r\n\r\nThe instant-search searchbox displays the native suggestions dropdown menu.\r\n\r\n**Bug: What is the expected behavior?**\r\n\r\nIt should not, adding `autocomplete=\"off\"` to the input.\r\n\r\n<img width=\"570\" alt=\"screen shot 2017-01-12 at 16 49 22\" src=\"https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/29529/21896595/3b89ac9a-d8e7-11e6-9be8-b1fafe0d6fed.png\">\r\n\r\nTested on https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/react/examples/e-commerce-infinite/",
